D5BAC1E54D37EBBD51393BB6DBFAE011: Change settings like knobs or toggles on another Patchwork device in a continuous pattern.

UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.AllowPortS: Determines if the Patchwork Tool can access any cable input or output ports on the device.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.EnabledOnP: Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled. Pre-game includes all phases prior to start of game (like the pre-game lobby or countdown to start of game.) This setting does not affect Edit Mode.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.Disable.De: Disables the device when an event occurs.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.Enable.Des: Enables the device when an event occurs.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.Shape.Desc: Modifies the modulation pattern of the selected waveform.
Please note: Use of a Patchwork audio device is limited to the creation of new and original musical works.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.Style.Desc: Selects the style for the chosen Rate, if it's not set to "Free." "Straight" will output at the set Rate, "Triplet" will output in a shuffle feel at two thirds of the Rate, and "Dotted" will output in a syncopated feel at one and a half times the Rate.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.BeatOffset: Sets a delay in the modulation timing after the beat. This knob appears on the device when Rate is set to any option other than â€œFree."
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.ModulatorO: Sets the destination for this device's Modulator Out cable.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.MaxIn.Desc: Sets the inputs for this device's Max knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.MinIn.Desc: Sets the inputs for this device's Min knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.OffsetIn.D: Sets the inputs for this device's Offset knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.RateIn.Des: Sets the inputs for this device's Rate carousel.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.ShapeIn.De: Sets the inputs for this device's Shape knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.SpeedIn.De: Sets the inputs for this device's Speed knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.StyleIn.De: Sets the inputs for this device's Style carousel.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.WaveShapeI: Sets the inputs for this device's Wave Shape carousel.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.BeatDurati: Sets the length of time for the LFO to output a cycle of the selected waveform. When set to "Free," use the Speed control to define the time.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.Max.Descri: Sets the maximum value of the modulation.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.Min.Descri: Sets the minimum value of the modulation.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.FreeHz.Des: Sets the rate of modulation in Hz (short for Hertz, the number of cycles per second.) This knob appears on the device when Rate is set to "Free."
Sets which waveform will be used to modulate the parameter value.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularWaveGenerator_C.OnDisabled: Triggers an event when the device is disabled.
Triggers an event when the device is enabled.
